{"tid":176267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮煒光：上屆梁振英就是高民望當選","createTime":"2017-03-28T05:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T13:07:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a226c3b84bc0fe9a3e157b27d98e284a8a62658b","tid":176267,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170328/s00001/c0155e04ddfc45d7dbadf3ddafee64f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170328%2Fs00001%2Fc0155e04ddfc45d7dbadf3ddafee64f3.jpg&h=89105e75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞統籌專員馮煒光於《都市日報》專欄撰文，提及勝出特首選舉的林鄭月娥的民意支持度不及另一候選人曾俊華高一事。他強調，曾俊華是泛民代表，「當泛民唯一支持一位候選人時，他的民望達到逾50%，有什麼稀奇？」<br />\n<br />\n專欄題為＜曾俊華是泛民代表＞，馮煒光指出，泛民在立法會選舉約拿到55%選票，所以當泛民唯一支持一位候選人時，他的民望超過50%，並不稀奇，「泛民不斷說曾俊華高票落選，只不過露了條尾巴：曾俊華徹頭徹尾的是泛民的代表。如果硬要說曾俊華高民望便應當選，那上屆梁振英就是高民望當選了」。<br />\n<br />\n馮煒光又說，今次選舉泛民不是根據信念和原則做人，「只不過是策反曾俊華，分化建制派」，形容這裏面充滿政治陰謀和計算。<br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英今早出席行政會議前亦談及特首選舉，指泛民主派有超過300名選委，卻不協調派人出選，認為他們錯失了機會，又反問曾俊華是否可代表他們。"},{"pid":"50789318dad12c36a92d8b85c98fefc8e400af7b","tid":176267,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170328/s00001/1490675462652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170328%2Fs00001%2F1490675462652&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=0d4d91e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170328%2Fs00001%2F1490675462652&h=b716cfee\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170328/s00001/1490675462652</a>"},{"pid":"f65db63eb03d2c1ee41cf0e6827dce42cf2d8094","tid":176267,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hk